# Precision Over Verbosity

## Rules

- Prefer short, explicit statements over long narrative explanations.
- Remove duplicated wording when the same rule already exists in a clearer location.
- Keep README and governance docs focused on repository purpose, structure, and decision boundaries.
- When replacing obsolete material, delete it instead of leaving parallel explanations behind.
